#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php
msgid "Simple Media Library Folders"
msgstr "Simple Media Library Folders"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php
msgid "https://rudrastyh.com/plugins/wordpress-media-library-folders"
msgstr "https://rudrastyh.com/plugins/wordpress-media-library-folders"

#. Description of the plugin
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php
msgid ""
"The plugin allows you to organize the WordPress media library in folders"
msgstr "Pluginet låter dig organisera WordPress mediebibliotek i mappar"

#. Author of the plugin
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php
msgid "Misha Rudrastyh"
msgstr "Misha Rudrastyh"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php
msgid "https://rudrastyh.com"
msgstr "https://rudrastyh.com"

#: classes/class-rudr-simple-upgrade.php:245
msgid ""
"It seems like your license key is expired or incorrect, please <a "
"href=\"%1$s\" target=\"_blank\">renew your license</a> in order to get the "
"latest plugin updates."
msgstr ""
"Det verkar som att din licensnyckel har gått ut eller är felaktig. <a "
"href=\"%1$s\" target=\"_blank\">Förnya din licens</a> för att få de senaste "
"pluginuppdateringarna."

#: classes/class-rudr-simple-upgrade.php:254
msgid ""
"Please set a license key in plugin settings in order to receive updates."
msgstr "Ange en licensnyckel i pluginets inställningar för att få uppdateringar."

#: classes/class-rudr-simple-upgrade.php:335
msgid ""
"Your personal license for <a href=\"%s\">%s</a> has expired. Please, <a "
"href=\"%s\">renew</a> or <a href=\"%s\">upgrade to lifetime</a> and forget "
"about this message."
msgstr ""
"Din personliga licens för <a href=\"%s\">%s</a> har gått ut. <a href=\"%s\">"
"Förnya</a> eller <a href=\"%s\">uppgradera till livstid</a> så slipper du "
"detta meddelande."

#: classes/class-rudr-simple-upgrade.php:365
msgid ""
"Please, set your license for <a href=\"%s\">%s</a> in the plugin settings, "
"<a href=\"%s\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Ange din licens för <a href=\"%s\">%s</a> i pluginets inställningar <a "
"href=\"%s\">här</a>."

#: classes/class-rudr-simple-upgrade.php:380
msgid ""
"It seems like you are not using a valid license for <a href=\"%s\">%s</a>. "
"Make sure it is set correctly <a href=\"%s\">in the plugin settings</a>."
msgstr ""
"Det verkar som att du inte använder en giltig licens för <a href=\"%s\">%s</"
"a>. Kontrollera att den är korrekt angiven <a href=\"%s\">i pluginets "
"inställningar</a>."

