#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:450
msgid ""
"You are about to permanently delete this folder from your site.\n"
"This action cannot be undone.\n"
"'Cancel' to stop, 'OK' to delete."
msgstr ""
"Du håller på att permanent ta bort den här mappen från webbplatsen.\n"
"Den här åtgärden kan inte ångras.\n"
"'Avbryt' för att stoppa, 'OK' för att ta bort."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:473
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:493
msgid "Media Library Folders Settings"
msgstr "Inställningar för mappar i mediebiblioteket"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:474
msgid "Media Library Folders"
msgstr "Mappar i mediebiblioteket"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:499
msgid "License"
msgstr "Licens"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:523
msgid "License Key"
msgstr "Licensnyckel"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:526
msgid ""
"License key is required to receive the latest plugin updates. Please note, "
"that your license key is the billing email you purchased the plugin with."
msgstr ""
"Licensnyckel krävs för att få de senaste pluginuppdateringarna. Observera att "
"din licensnyckel är den e-postadress för fakturering som du använde när du "
"köpte pluginet."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:532
msgid ""
"It seems that before you used the following media library folder plugins. "
"You can import their data or completely remove it from the database."
msgstr ""
"Det verkar som att du tidigare har använt följande pluginer för mappar i "
"mediebiblioteket. Du kan importera deras data eller ta bort den helt från "
"databasen."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:551
msgid "Run import"
msgstr "Kör import"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:552
msgid "Delete plugin data"
msgstr "Ta bort pluginets data"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:556
msgid "1 folder"
msgid_plural "%s folders"
msgstr[0] "1 mapp"
msgstr[1] "%s mappar"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:556
msgid "with 1 associated media file found to import"
msgid_plural "with %s associated media files found to import"
msgstr[0] "där 1 tillhörande mediefil hittades för import"
msgstr[1] "där %s tillhörande mediefiler hittades för import"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:568
#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:1178
msgid "Allowed Roles"
msgstr "Tillåtna roller"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:582
msgid "Manage what user roles are allowed to manage media library folders."
msgstr "Hantera vilka användarroller som får hantera mappar i mediebiblioteket."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:587
msgid "Show Count"
msgstr "Visa antal"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:590
msgid ""
"This option allows you to show the total number of files in every folder."
msgstr "Det här alternativet låter dig visa det totala antalet filer i varje mapp."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:594
msgid "Show In List View"
msgstr "Visa i listvy"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:597
msgid ""
"By default, the folders are only displayed in the grid view to keep the "
"Media Library page nice and clean."
msgstr ""
"Som standard visas mapparna bara i rutnätsvyn för att hålla sidan "
"Mediebiblioteket ren och överskådlig."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:601
msgid "Show In Media Modals"
msgstr "Visa i mediedialoger"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:604
msgid ""
"By default, only a simple filter by folder is available, but with this "
"option you can display the entire folder sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Som standard finns bara ett enkelt filter efter mapp, men med det här "
"alternativet kan du visa hela sidopanelen för mappar."

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:608
msgid "Delete Media Files with a Folder"
msgstr "Ta bort mediefiler tillsammans med en mapp"

#: rudr-simple-media-library-folders.php:611
msgid ""
"With this option selected, when you delete a folder, all the media files in "
"this folder will be deleted as well."
msgstr ""
"Om detta alternativ är valt tas alla mediefiler i mappen också bort när du "
"tar bort mappen."

